    {
      "parameters": {
        "modelId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "models/gemini-2.0-flash-exp",
          "mode": "list"
        },
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are an expert B2B sales copywriter specializing in AI automation and business growth services.\n\n## CONTEXT\nClient Name: {{ $json.firstName }}\nFull Name: {{ $json.fullName }}\nCompany: {{ $json.companyName || 'their business' }}\nIndustry: {{ $json.industry || 'their industry' }}\nLinkedIn: {{ $json.linkedinUrl || 'N/A' }}\n\n## YOUR TASK\nWrite a highly personalized cold email that:\n1. Addresses the recipient by first name\n2. References their company/industry if available\n3. Identifies a specific pain point relevant to their business\n4. Presents AI automation as the solution\n5. Demonstrates credibility with a brief case study or statistic\n6. Includes a clear call-to-action for booking a discovery call\n\n## EMAIL REQUIREMENTS\n- Length: 150-200 words\n- Tone: Professional, consultative, confident (not pushy)\n- Structure: Problem → Solution → Proof → Call-to-Action\n- Include a compelling subject line\n- Mention specific benefits: 10X revenue growth potential, 70% time savings, or improved operational efficiency\n\n## FORMATTING RULES\n- Start with: **Subject:** [your subject line]\n- Use short paragraphs (2-3 sentences max)\n- Include ONE specific metric or case study\n- End with a scheduling link placeholder: [BOOK A CALL]\n- Sign off professionally\n\n## WRITING STYLE\n- Use active voice\n- Be specific, not generic\n- Focus on business outcomes, not technical features\n- Create urgency without being aggressive\n- Sound like a trusted advisor, not a salesperson\n\n## WHAT TO AVOID\n- Emojis or casual language\n- Multiple CTAs\n- Overpromising or hype\n- Technical jargon\n- Generic templates\n\nNow write the email."
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.7
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.googleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        -112,
        -16
      ],
      "id": "226cf770-5de7-4e2c-9c78-48e5101b1987",
      "name": "Generate Personalized Email",
      "credentials": {
        "googlePalmApi": {
          "id": "SgSXLURnz7IswDf0",
          "name": "Google Gemini(PaLM) Api account 2"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Extract email content from AI response\nconst response = $input.first().json;\nconst content = response.content?.parts?.[0]?.text || response.text || '';\n\nif (!content) {\n  throw new Error('AI did not generate email content');\n}\n\n// Parse subject and body\nconst subjectMatch = content.match(/\\*\\*Subject:\\*\\*\\s*(.+?)(?:\\n|$)/i);\nconst subject = subjectMatch ? subjectMatch[1].trim() : 'AI Automation Can 10X Your Business Growth';\n\n// Remove subject line and metadata from body\nlet body = content\n  .replace(/\\*\\*Subject:\\*\\*.*?(?:\\n|$)/i, '')\n  .trim();\n\n// Replace placeholder with actual booking link\nconst bookingLink = 'https://calendly.com/your-company/discovery-call'; // Replace with your actual link\nbody = body.replace(/\\[BOOK A CALL\\]/gi, bookingLink);\n\n// Get lead data from previous node\nconst leadData = $('Normalize Lead Data').first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    subject,\n    body,\n    to: leadData.email,\n    firstName: leadData.firstName,\n    fullName: leadData.fullName,\n    rowNumber: leadData.rowNumber\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        208,
        -16
      ],
      "id": "61523aca-a8bd-4133-a62f-948aa7082e46",
      "name": "Parse Email Content"
